Under the game object, go to &quot;Commands&quot;. Add a new command, and for the command pattern, make it [i:3ojm9cpc]help[/i:3ojm9cpc].

If you're on the code viewer, something like this..
[code:3ojm9cpc]&lt;command name=&quot;help1&quot;&gt;
  &lt;pattern&gt;help&lt;/pattern&gt;
  &lt;script&gt;&lt;!&#91;CDATA&#91;
    //whatever script here
  &#93;&#93;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
&lt;/command&gt;[/code:3ojm9cpc]
